<header class="site-header">
	<div class="logo-wrap">
		<span class="logo-mark"></span>
		<strong>Redirect Lab</strong>
	</div>
	<nav class="site-nav">
		<a href="/">Home</a>
		<a href="/forms">Form Lab</a>
		<a href="/journey">Journey</a>
		<a href="/flaky">Flaky Lab</a>
	</nav>
</header>

<main>
	<section class="hero">
		<p class="eyebrow">Scenario: Redirect Workflows</p>
		<h1>Automate direct, delayed, and conditional redirects.</h1>
		<p class="hero-copy">
			Use this page to assert URL changes, waits, and behavior after navigation events.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="panel split-panel">
		<div class="panel-box">
			<h2>Immediate redirects</h2>
			<p class="small-note">Useful for validating href and location change assertions.</p>
			<div class="hero-actions">
				<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/result?source=anchor-redirect" data-testid="anchor-redirect-link">
					Go to Result (Anchor)
				</a>
				<a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/go?to=/result?source=server-redirect" data-testid="server-redirect-link">
					Go via /go route
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="panel-box">
			<h2>Delayed and conditional redirects</h2>
			<p id="redirectStatus" class="small-note" data-testid="redirect-status">No action triggered yet.</p>
			<div class="hero-actions">
				<button
					id="delayedRedirectBtn"
					type="button"
					class="btn btn-primary"
					data-url="/result?source=delayed-button"
					data-testid="delayed-redirect-btn"
				>
					Redirect after random delay
				</button>
				<button id="conditionalRedirectBtn" type="button" class="btn btn-ghost" data-testid="conditional-redirect-btn">
					Redirect only if ping succeeds
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="panel">
		<h2>Expected outcomes</h2>
		<ul class="check-grid">
			<li>Immediate anchor goes to /result with query source=anchor-redirect.</li>
			<li>Server redirect goes through /go and lands on /result.</li>
			<li>Delayed button redirects after random 400-2200ms.</li>
			<li>Conditional button may fail because /api/flaky/ping can return 500.</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
	<p>Playwright Practice Platform <%= launchYear %>. Redirect timing scenario.</p>
</footer>
